#

Classic Black Bean Burger

35 min
$5
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

EggDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodGrillHealthy

Description

A hearty and satisfying black bean burger that’s quick to prepare and packed with flavor!

Ingredients

  • canned black beans: 1 (15 oz) can
  • bread crumbs: 1/2 cup
  • egg: 1
  • green bell pepper: 1/2, diced
  • onion: 1/4, finely chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • cheddar cheese: 1/4 cup, shredded
  • burger buns: 2
  • lettuce: 2 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • avocado: 1/2, sliced
